#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/xml/intro.rst:8
msgid ""
"LVGL Pro is a complete toolkit to build, test, share, and ship embedded "
"UIs efficiently."
msgstr "LVGL Pro è un toolkit completo per creare, testare, condividere e distribuire interfacce utente integrate in modo efficiente."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/xml/intro.rst:11
